    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The primary validation result demonstrates RH prediction error of 11.3% against the FDA benchmark, within the 15% acceptance criterion, and correctly identifies worst-case operating conditions. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements for a Class II device with medium model influence. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the decision that the CFD model may be used to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device.",
